Parliament, Thursday, 6 May 2021 – The Portfolio Committee on Sports, Arts and Culture will tomorrow receive a briefing from the South African Football Association (SAFA) on issues that include challenges faced by the national football team, Bafana Bafana, grassroots development plans and women’s football.
	
	Details of the briefing are as follows:
	
	Date: Friday, 7 May 2021
	Time: 9h00
	Venue: Zoom platform
	
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES.
	
	For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer:
